images.title: A slow reminder for a fast world
images.caption: Manatee Awareness Month
images.desc: November isn't just about turkey dinners and pumpkin pie—it's also Manatee Awareness Month, when we show some love to the ocean's chillest stars. Forget dolphins doing flips or sharks stealing headlines—manatees win hearts by doing, well, almost nothing. And that's the charm.
